descript.abstract: This is the County of San Diego, Department of Parks and Recreation polygon Parks_CN layer. This layer represents County Park-specific owned, co-owned, leased, funded or cooperatively managed park units. Because this dataset includes managed, leased or co-owned properties, overlap with other property owners or management agencies will be apparent if using similar parcel-based layers.
descript.purpose: Parks_CN is used by the Department of Parks and Recreation as an inventory and management tool of County Park properties.
